OL,3,CMaro Itoje 'deeply honoured' after
OL,4,Cbeing named British and Irish Lions
OL,5,Ccaptain
OL,7,FMaro Itoje has become the first
OL,8,FEnglish captain of the British and
OL,9,FIrish Lions since Martin Johnson in
OL,10,F2001 after being placed in charge of
OL,11,Fthe squad bound for Australia this
OL,12,Fsummer.
OL,14,FHead coach Andy Farrell has turned to
OL,15,Fthe Camden-born star after he
OL,16,Fimpressed while leading England during
OL,17,Fthis year's Six Nations, helping his
OL,18,Fteam finish runners-up.
