OL,3,CMaro Itoje 'deeply honoured' after
OL,4,Cbeing named British and Irish Lions
OL,5,Ccaptain
OL,7,FThe 93-cap Saracens second row, who
OL,8,Fhas also made six Test appearances for
OL,9,Fthe Lions, was presented on stage at
OL,10,FThe O2 in London where Farrell named
OL,11,Fhis squad for the 10-fixture itinerary.
OL,13,F"It feels amazing to be named Lions
OL,14,Fcaptain," said Itoje, who revealed
OL,15,Fthat he found out the news when
OL,16,FFarrell called him on Tuesday.
