OL,3,CMaro Itoje 'deeply honoured' after
OL,4,Cbeing named British and Irish Lions
OL,5,Ccaptain
OL,7,F"I'm deeply honoured, humbled and I'll
OL,8,Fdo my best to do the role justice. I'm
OL,9,Fvery much looking forward to the
OL,10,Fchallenge ahead, it's going to be a
OL,11,Fgreat tour.
OL,13,F"I know the appetite amongst the
OL,14,Fplayers is extremely high, everyone is
OL,15,Fhungry to be a Lion and I can't wait
OL,16,Fto play my role."
