OL,3,CMaro Itoje 'deeply honoured' after
OL,4,Cbeing named British and Irish Lions
OL,5,Ccaptain
OL,7,FItoje's leadership credentials were
OL,8,Fonce questioned by former England head
OL,9,Fcoach Eddie Jones, who in 2021
OL,10,Fdescribed the 30-year-old as "very
OL,11,Finward-looking" and added that he
OL,12,F"doesn't usually influence people off
OL,13,Fthe field".
OL,15,FBut he has disproved that assessment
OL,16,Fthis season by taking charge of
OL,17,FSaracens, England and now the Lions.
