OL,3,CMaro Itoje 'deeply honoured' after
OL,4,Cbeing named British and Irish Lions
OL,5,Ccaptain
OL,7,FAs an automatic pick for the Test team
OL,8,Fand standout performer on the last two
OL,9,Ftours by the elite of British and
OL,10,FIrish rugby, he has been the
OL,11,Foutstanding candidate since the Six
OL,12,FNations.
OL,14,F"The captain is the beacon, he is the
OL,15,Fleader and he is the person that
OL,16,Feverybody looks up to. It takes a
OL,17,Fspecial person, that's for sure,"
OL,18,FFarrell said.
